---
title: Seared Steak & Roasted Kūmara Toss with Garlic Yoghurt Dressing
description: Wholesome roasted veggies and a juicy cut of rump steak - what could be more delish? It's topped with a creamy garlic yoghurt to keep it low in calories (and carbs!), so you'll be licking the plate clean without any of the guilt.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
